author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Five Prime Therapeutics To Close Bladder Cancer Cohort Of Its Phase 1 FPA144-001 Trial
text:
April 10, 2018 / 4:58 PM / Updated 25 minutes ago BRIEF-Five Prime Therapeutics To Close Bladder Cancer Cohort Of Its Phase 1 FPA144-001 Trial Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 10 (Reuters) - Five Prime Therapeutics Inc: 
* TO CLOSE BLADDER CANCER COHORT OF PHASE 1 TRIAL EVALUATING BEMARITUZUMAB TREATING PATIENTS WHOSE TUMORS OVEREXPRESS FGFR2B PROTEIN 
* SAYS TO CONTINUE TREATING BLADDER CANCER PATIENTS CURRENTLY ON STUDY BUT WILL NOT ENROLL ADDITIONAL PATIENTS IN COHORT-SEC FILING Source text: ( bit.ly/2HnAIag ) Further company coverage:
